{"id":285928,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-昆明市民提议发起抗议px项目落户游行示威/","date":"2013-03-25T09:46:25Z","modified":"2013-03-25T09:46:25Z","title":"维权网 | 昆明市民提议发起抗议PX项目落户游行示威","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span><span></span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）近日来，关于</span>PX</span></span><span><span>项目落户昆明的消息收到当地市民的广泛关注。有市民拨打了市长热线，随后市长热线给该市民回电话，说最近很多市民打电话问</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span></span><span><span>项目的事情，问该市民有什么建议。市民表示：第一，目前网上到处都在传，希望政府出面说一下是不是确有其事，如果有，这个项目到底有些什么危害？第二，如果是早就定下的项目，是否有过听证，希望政府能公开听证材料。市长热线说会再联系。</span></span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>有昆明市民质疑说，既然可以在政府工作报告（</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span></span><span><span>年）第一段显要的位置写明的“石油炼化基地”，并且已经是在建设之中，为何在环保部的公示信息中没有提到半个字？如何通过的环保审批？</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span></span><span><span>日</span></span><span><span>，昆明网友郑楔健发布帖子，表示为抗议</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span></span><span><span>项目落户昆明，将向昆明公安局提起游行集会示威相关申请，游行时间为</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span></span><span><span>年</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></span><span><span>日</span></span><span><span>中午</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span></span><span><span>点起至</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span></span><span><span>点，地点为：昆明五华区</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span><span><span>南坪步行街</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span><span><span>正义路街口。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>郑楔健表示，本次活动秉持理性平和之精神，口号为反对</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span></span><span><span>项目落户昆明污染环境，示威设备包括便携扩音器</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></span><span><span>个，示威方式包括散步或者开阔空间静坐。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><span><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iyhQwSafLW4/UVAD-CL7BfI/AAAAAAAAfQE/8BZeKi8swcE/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iyhQwSafLW4/UVAD-CL7BfI/AAAAAAAAfQE/8BZeKi8swcE/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"253\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><span><br /></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[15021,19196]}